Iron, Magnesium, Vitamin D, and Zinc Deficiencies  
in Children Presenting with Symptoms of  
Attention-Deficit/Hyperactivity Disorder 
Amelia Villagomez 1,* and Ujjwal Ramtekkar 2  
1 University of Arizona, 2800 E. Ajo Way Suite 300, Tucson, AZ 85713, USA  
2 Mercy Children’s Hospital, 621 S. New Ballas Road, Suite 693A, Saint Louis, MO 63141, USA;  
E-Mail: ujjwal.ramtekkar@mercy.net 
